race.comment: JAN'S MEMORY (3) boasts a strong record this course with 13 wins and eight minors from 39 tries. Was out of placings last time (22.95) at this track in a NG, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ZIPPING CLAVELL (2) was below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.13) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length fifth. Already a winner from this draw. Can hit the frame with the right run. HENDRIX (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 8 length fifth (23.15) but scored five back at this track (23.05). Comes through a solid form race last start. One of the main contenders. ROSACKY RAYO (6) is a last start winner who rates one of the chances again.
